contains 禾 hé ‘grain; crops’ (coincidentally homophonous with 和). It is also 
seen in 科 and 種. 否 fǒu, often used instead of the ‘or not’ part of the V-not-V 
pattern in written communication, is a late creation, with 不 suggesting the 
meaning.  
